{"tid":639002,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今天不買樓，明天更加買唔到","createTime":"2018-04-23T07:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T08:12:54.000Z","uid":10101,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54781441fa512356c27a64e78d88b020b2f713b5","tid":639002,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"1. 加息，貿易戰消息已經消化左，不會影響樓市<br />\n2. 香港地太有錢，雖然收租回報低，但只要樓價日日升便無問題<br />\n3. 大部分人月供一萬五千至兩萬五，唔夠錢，最多咪食少餐<br />\n4. 仲有父幹同埋高成數按揭，樓價便一定有承托力<br />\n5. 2017年升左16%，所以我估2018年會升10%，今天不買，明天便會貴多10%<br />\n6. 除左核爆，唸唔到有跌既理由<br />\n<br />\n同意請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a65f3c209061840d0bcc10d4edda3260e71676","tid":639002,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"岩呀 唔買正傻仔 買唔起都係"},{"pid":"27c671cb82622ff13fd46200338a3be790ede56b","tid":639002,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"岩丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b90c665ed3e536de54c683f9c3de170e190cc3","tid":639002,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"即刻去買先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}